Before making any changes to this project:

1. Read CLAUDE.md in the project root completely.
2. Check STABILIZATION_PLAN.md to see which phase and step are active.
3. Only work on the current phase and step. Do not skip ahead.
4. Make single-layer changes only. Do not modify multiple layers at once.
5. Run py_compile on any file you modify before finishing.
6. Run the required verification for the active plan step before and after code changes when applicable.
7. After completing a step, remind the user to review git diff and commit with:
   git add -A
   git commit -m "phase X stepY: description"

If you are unsure about anything, stop and ask.
